org.hibernate.sql.results.spi

Interface SqlSelection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SqlSelectionGroupNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResolvingSqlSelectionImpl

    public interface SqlSelection
extends SqlSelectionGroupNode
    Represents a selection at the SQL/JDBC level. Essentially made up of: getJdbcValueExtractor():: How to read a value from JDBC (conceptually similar to a method reference) getValuesArrayPosition():: The position for this selection in relation to the "JDBC values array" (see RowProcessingState.getJdbcValue(org.hibernate.sql.results.spi.SqlSelection)) getJdbcResultSetIndex():: The position for this selection in relation to the JDBC object (ResultSet, etc)
